{"id":256631,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/奇闻录-莫言发声为磕巴/","date":"2012-10-12T09:01:18Z","modified":"2012-10-16T07:42:45Z","title":"奇闻录 | 莫言发声为磕巴","content":"<p><p>今天（10月12日），2012年诺贝尔文学家获得者莫言在他的家乡山东高密，告诉路透社记者，他期望2010年诺贝尔和平奖得主刘大磕巴“能够尽快获得自由”（&#8221;I hope he can achieve his freedom as soon as possible&#8221;）<span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/liu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"A visitor stands in front of a photograph of Nobel Laureate Liu Xiaobo carrying a puppet, taken by his wife Liu Xia, during her photo exhibition in Hong Kong\" width=\"450\" height=\"357\" /></p>\n<p>现年57岁的莫言还表示，他八十年代时就读过刘大磕巴的文学批评作品，但他对刘转向政治领域感到不解。</p>\n<p>此前，一些作家、维权人士和媒体曾因莫言超写过毛泽东在延安文艺座谈会上的讲话而批评他不配得诺贝尔文学奖。</p>\n<p>来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/12/us-china-moyan-idUSBRE89B0CM20121012\">路透社</a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=Hguu6TPrJO0:OwlHKm-1t7I:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=Hguu6TPrJO0:OwlHKm-1t7I:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=Hguu6TPrJO0:OwlHKm-1t7I:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=Hguu6TPrJO0:OwlHKm-1t7I:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=Hguu6TPrJO0:OwlHKm-1t7I:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=Hguu6TPrJO0:OwlHKm-1t7I:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=Hguu6TPrJO0:OwlHKm-1t7I:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/qi-wen-lu/~4/Hguu6TPrJO0\" height=\"1\